.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-INFO-JSON" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-info-json \- show wallet metadata as JSON
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-info-json
.I wallet_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns wallet metadata from the database as structured JSON.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"wallet":"<name>", "meta":{...}, "db_path":"<path>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-info (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-list (1)
